<h3>Edit Publication</h3>
<br> &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp

<form method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="../EditConfPro"  onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to update the journal ?');"> 
	<p>
<font color = 'blue'>
	 <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span> IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-hand-down"></span>
<br><br>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp
1. All fields are mandatory.<br>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp
